Cell["\<\
Blade: a pacakge for block-triangular form improved Feynman integral \
decomposition.
Version 2024/05/23.
Author: Xin Guan, Xiao Liu, Yan-Qing Ma and Wen-Hao Wu.
Number of defined symbols=68. Please see ?Blade`* for help.

--------------------------------------------------
BLSetReducerOptions->\"IBPParameter\" -> Automatic, \"IntegralOrdering\" -> \
1, \"CheckMastersQ\" -> True, \"FilterLevel\" -> 3, \"IBPForMapSector\" -> \
False, \"MaxIncrement\" -> 2, \"CloseSymmetry\" -> False, \
\"ExternalSymmetry\" -> True, \"CutNoDot\" -> False, \"BlackBoxRank\" -> 2, \
\"BlackBoxDot\" -> 0, \"MaxPrime\" -> 200, \"MaxDegree\" -> 1000, \
\"Reconstructor\" -> \"FiniteFlow\"
BLSetSchemeOptions->\"OperatorExtendGQ\" -> True, \"MinimalSchemeRank\" -> 1, \
\"PartitionDot\" -> True, \"PartitionRankThreshold\" -> 100, \
\"UniqueSubsectorQ\" -> True\
\>", "Print",
